| 4ct | [G-VS1 GIA Excellent](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/27666919?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | $58,110 | $14,528 | 4.5× |
| 5ct | [E-VS2 GIA Excellent](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/23555936?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | $147,110 | $30,332 | 9.4× |
