| [IGI 4ct D-VVS1](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28884761?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | D-VVS1 | $9,680 | 10.3mm | ~4ct natural |
| [IGI 5ct D-VVS1](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29116650?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | D-VVS1 | $12,730 | 11.0mm | ~5ct natural |
